comments.body:
I'm wondering if maybe this would work:

``` ts
interface GulpIstanbul {
    (opts?: Options): NodeJS.ReadWriteStream; // istanbul(opts);
    hookRequire(): NodeJS.ReadWriteStream; // istanbul.hookRequire();
    summarizeCoverage(...): Coverage;
    writeReports(...): NodeJS.ReadWriteStream;
}
```

It's confusing that `GulpIstanbul` is both a function and a module :S

